sequenceDiagram
    participant Phone
    participant Tailscale
    participant Daemon as FastAPI Daemon
    participant SAL
    participant Local as Local Model
    Phone->>Tailscale: Command (private overlay)
    Tailscale->>Daemon: Route to M1 Mac
    Daemon->>SAL: Compose prompt (budget-fit)
    SAL->>Local: Execute on MLX
    Local-->>SAL: Result
    SAL-->>Daemon: Structured output
    Daemon-->>Phone: Response over Tailscale
